 v_x^{\text{even}}(s) \triangleq \frac{v_x(s)+v_x(-s)}{2} \qquad \text{and} \qquad v_x^{\text{odd}}(s) \triangleq \frac{v_x(s)-v_x(-s)}{2}. 
